actions.message:
```
*Help                      Lists available commands
*Kick [@user] [reason]     Kicks the mentioned user
*Ban [@user] [reason]      Bans the mentioned user
*Mute [@user]              Mutes the mentioned user (vc)
*Unmute [@user]            Unmutes the mentioned user
*DeleteChannel [#channel]  Deletes the mentioned channel
*DeleteRole [#channel]     Deletes the mentioned role
*Purge [amount]            Deletes the mentioned amount of messages
*Warn [@user] [reason]     Warns the mentioned user
*Lockdown                  Locks down the channel
*tLockdown [minutes]       Locks down the channel for specified time
*Open                      Opens up the channel
```
